CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `crm_order` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `ORDER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `ORDER_STATUS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CUSTOMER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `DEMAND_CONTACT_PERSON` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DEMAND_CONTACT_PERSON_TEL` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DEMAND_CONTACT_PERSON_MOBILE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DEMAND_CONTACT_PERSON_FAX` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DEMAND_PAY_TIME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DEMAND_PAY_TYPE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `DEMAND_PAY_FEE_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `DEMAND_GATHER_TYPE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DEMAND_GATHER_TIME` date NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01',
  `DEMAND_GATHER_METHOD` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DEMAND_INVOICE_TYPE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `GATHERED_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `UNGATHER_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `ACCOMPLISH_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `LIST_PRICE_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `SALE_PRICE_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `COST_PRICE_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `RETURN_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `GATHER_PERIOD` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',

--
-- 表的结构 `crm_ordering`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `crm_ordering` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `REASON` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `PRODUCT_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `AMOUNT` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `UNIT` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SUBTOTAL` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `PAY_SHIP_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `INVOICE_INFO_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `GATHER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `REAL_CUSTOMER_MAILING_ADDRESS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REAL_CONTACT_PERSON` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REAL_CONTACT_PERSON_TEL` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REAL_CONTACT_PERSON_FAX` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `GATHER_GROUP` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `GATHER_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `REAL_INVOICE_TIME` date NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01',
  `REAL_GATHER_TIME` date NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01',
  `REAL_PAY_TIME` date NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01',
  `CHECK_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `REAL_GATHER_TYPE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REAL_GATHER_METHOD` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REAL_PAY_FEE_TYPE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REAL_PAY_FEE_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `REAL_PAY_TYPE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REAL_INVOICE_TYPE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REMARK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `WHICH_TIME` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `REGISTER_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `INVOICE_DRA_TAG` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',

--
-- 表的结构 `crm_workflow`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `crm_workflow` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `config_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `object_id` char(30) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE1` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE2` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `checker_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `checker` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `check_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `WHICH_TIME` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=9 ;

  `DESCRIBE3` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE4` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `COUNTER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

--
-- 表的结构 `design_file`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `design_file` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `PRODUCT_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PRODUCT_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PRODUCT_NICK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PRODUCT_CLASS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `type` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `product_length` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `spec_top` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `spec_bottom` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `drawing_top` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `drawing_bottom` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `drawing_lron` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `product_pallet_sf` varchar(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `AMOUNT_UNIT` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PRODUCT_DESCRIBE` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FACTORY_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FACTORY_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PROVIDER_GROUP` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PHOTO1` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PHOTO2` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `WARRANTY` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `LIST_PRICE` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `COST_PRICE` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `REAL_COST_PRICE` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `LIFECYCLE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PERSONAL_UNIT` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PERSONAL_VALUE` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `TWIN_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `TWIN_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REMARK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ACHIEVEMENT_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `ATTACHMENT_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `RETURN_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `RETURN_AMOUNT` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `FILE_CHANGE_AMOUNT` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `USED_PRODUCT_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `RESPONSIBLE_PERSON_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `RESPONSIBLE_PERSON_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHANGER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHANGER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHECK_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHANGE_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `LATELY_CHANGE_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `LATELY_TRADE_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `DELETE_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `RECOVERY_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `MODIFY_TAG` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `EXCEL_TAG` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `EXCEL_TAG2` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `EXCEL_TAG3` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `EXCEL_TAG4` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `DESIGN_MODULE_TAG` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `DESIGN_PROCEDURE_TAG` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `DESIGN_CELL_TAG` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `RECOMMEND_PROVIDER_TAG` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PRICE_CHANGE_TAG` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PRICE_ALARM_TAG` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ORDER_SALE_BONUS_RATE` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `ORDER_PROFIT_BONUS_RATE` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `RETAIL_SALE_BONUS_RATE` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `RETAIL_PROFIT_BONUS_RATE` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `COST_CALCULATE_TYPE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '移动加权平均',
  `SERIAL_NUMBER_TAG` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `CALCULATE_BONUS_SN_TAG` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '否',
  `promotion` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `opinion` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `promotion2` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `opinion2` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `promotion3` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `opinion3` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `opinion4` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `recommend_logistics_tag` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PURCHASE_QCS_WAY` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `INTRMANU_QCS_WAY` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CRM_DELIVER_QCS_WAY` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `MANU_PROCEDURE_QCS_WAY` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `STOCK_QCS_WAY` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `OTHER_QCS_WAY` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `QCS_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `QCS_APPLY_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `CHAIN_ID` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHAIN_NAME` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE1` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `C_DEFINE2` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE3` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE4` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE5` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE6` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE7` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE8` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `C_DEFINE10` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE11` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE12` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE13` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE14` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE15` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE16` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE17` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE18` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE19` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE20` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `GAR_TAG` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `USED_TAG` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `excel_batch_tag` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)

--
-- 表的结构 `design_file_dig`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `design_file_dig` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `PRODUCT_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PRODUCT_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PRODUCT_NICK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PRODUCT_CLASS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

--
-- 表的结构 `document_db`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `document_db` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `object` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `range` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reader` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reference` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `comment` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment1` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment2` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `runtime` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment3` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment4` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `standard` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment5` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment6` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `logic` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment7` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment8` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `physical` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment9` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment10` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `security` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment11` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment12` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `efficiency` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment13` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment14` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `remark` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `lately_change_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `register_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `change_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `register` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `changer` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `change_amount` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `doc_id` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `doc_ver` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

-- 导出表中的数据 `document_db`

  `attachment1` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment2` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `attachment7` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `attachment9` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `change_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `register` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `changer` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `doc_ver` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=230 ;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `document_firstpart`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `document_firstpart` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `first_kind_id` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `first_kind_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `filesystem` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `attachment12` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `dbsystem` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `document_multilanguage_dig` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `tablename` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `name` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `name_chinese` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `lately_change_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `register_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `change_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `register` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `changer` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `change_amount` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `comment_tag` tinyint(3) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

-- 表的结构 `document_otherprogram`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `document_otherprogram` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `name` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `type` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `directory` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `human_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `topic` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `standard` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment1` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment2` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `content` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment3` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment4` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `comment` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment5` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment6` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `tech` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `skill` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `sentiment` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `remark` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `lately_change_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `change_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `register_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `register` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `changer` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `change_amount` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `doc_id` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `doc_ver` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `file_length` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `init_tag` tinyint(3) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- 表的结构 `document_salary`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `document_salary` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `SALARY_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PAY_TIMES` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `HUMAN_AMOUNT` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `SALARY_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `SALARY_STANDARD_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `REGISTER_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `PAID_SALARY_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `SALARY_PAY_TYPE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `EXCEL_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '2',
  `PAY_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `REGISTER_FINISH_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- 导出表中的数据 `document_salary`
--


-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `document_salary_human_details`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `document_salary_human_details` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `SALARY_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FIRST_KIND_ID` char(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FIRST_KIND_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SECOND_KIND_ID` char(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SECOND_KIND_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `THIRD_KIND_ID` char(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `THIRD_KIND_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DETAILS_NUMBER` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `SALARY_STANDARD_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `STANDARD_SALARY_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `DEDUCT_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `BONUS_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `SALARY_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `SALE_BONUS_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

-- 导出表中的数据 `document_salary_human_details`

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `document_salary_human_details_details`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `document_salary_human_details_details` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `SALARY_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `ITEM_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `ITEM_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SALARY` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- 导出表中的数据 `document_salary_human_details_details`
--


-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `document_salary_standard`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `document_salary_standard` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `STANDARD_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `STANDARD_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `MAJOR_TYPE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESIGNER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESIGNER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHANGER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHANGER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECK_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `REGISTER_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHANGE_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `SALARY_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `REMARK` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `EXCEL_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '2',
  `CHANGE_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- 导出表中的数据 `document_salary_standard`
--


-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `document_salary_standard_details`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `document_salary_standard_details` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `STANDARD_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `STANDARD_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DETAILS_NUMBER` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ITEM_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `ITEM_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SALARY` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- 导出表中的数据 `document_salary_standard_details`
--


-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `document_salary_unit_details`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `document_salary_unit_details` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `SALARY_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FIRST_KIND_ID` char(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FIRST_KIND_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SECOND_KIND_ID` char(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SECOND_KIND_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `THIRD_KIND_ID` char(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `THIRD_KIND_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_AMOUNT` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `SALARY_STANDARD_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `SALARY_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `PAID_SALARY_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `REGISTER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECK_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `REGISTER_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `REMARK` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `EXCEL_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '2',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- 导出表中的数据 `document_salary_unit_details`
--


-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `document_second`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `document_second` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `main_code` char(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `first_code` char(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `second_code` char(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '00',
  `main_kind_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `main_kind_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `first_kind_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `first_kind_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `second_kind_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `second_kind_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `module_tag` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `picture` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `topic` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `object` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `range` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reader` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reference` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `comment` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment1` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment2` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `standard` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment3` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment4` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `mains` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment5` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment6` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `relation` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment7` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment8` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `function` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment9` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment10` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `filesystem` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment11` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment12` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `dbsystem` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment13` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment14` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `remark` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `lately_change_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `register_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `change_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `register` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `changer` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `change_amount` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `doc_id` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `doc_ver` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `head_file` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `task_tag` tinyint(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1774 ;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `document_secondpart`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `document_secondpart` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `main_kind_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `main_kind_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `first_kind_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `first_kind_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `second_kind_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `second_kind_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `module_tag` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `topic` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `object` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `range` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reader` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reference` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `comment` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment1` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment2` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `standard` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment3` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment4` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `mains` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment5` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment6` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `relation` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment7` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment8` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `function` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment9` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment10` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `filesystem` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment11` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment12` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `dbsystem` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment13` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment14` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `remark` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `lately_change_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `register_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `change_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `register` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `changer` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `change_amount` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `doc_id` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `doc_ver` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `head_file` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- 导出表中的数据 `document_secondpart`
--


-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `document_secondpart_dig`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `document_secondpart_dig` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `main_kind_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `main_kind_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `first_kind_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `first_kind_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `second_kind_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `second_kind_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `module_tag` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `topic` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `object` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `range` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reader` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reference` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `comment` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment1` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment2` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `standard` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment3` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment4` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `mains` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment5` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment6` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `relation` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment7` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment8` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `function` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment9` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment10` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `filesystem` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment11` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment12` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `dbsystem` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment13` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment14` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `remark` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `lately_change_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `register_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `change_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `register` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `changer` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `change_amount` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `doc_id` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `doc_ver` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `head_file` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- 导出表中的数据 `document_secondpart_dig`
--


-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `document_secondpart_temp`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `document_secondpart_temp` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `main_kind_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `main_kind_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `first_kind_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `first_kind_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `second_kind_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `second_kind_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `module_tag` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `topic` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `object` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `range` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reader` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reference` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `comment` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment1` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment2` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `standard` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment3` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment4` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `mains` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment5` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment6` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `relation` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment7` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment8` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `function` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment9` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment10` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `filesystem` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `CHECKER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHANGER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

--
-- 表的结构 `document_techfile`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `document_techfile` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `FIRST_KIND_ID` char(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FIRST_KIND_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SECOND_KIND_ID` char(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SECOND_KIND_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `THIRD_KIND_ID` char(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `THIRD_KIND_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_ADDRESS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_POSTCODE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_TITLE_CLASS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_MAJOR_FIRST_KIND_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_MAJOR_FIRST_KIND_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_MAJOR_SECOND_KIND_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_MAJOR_SECOND_KIND_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_BANK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_ACCOUNT` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_TEL` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_HOME_TEL` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_CELLPHONE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_EMAIL` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HOBBY` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SPECIALITY` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SEX` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `RELIGION` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PARTY` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `NATIONALITY` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `RACE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `BIRTHDAY` date NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01',
  `BIRTHPLACE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `AGE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `EDUCATED_DEGREE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `EDUCATED_YEARS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `EDUCATED_MAJOR` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SIN` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `IDCARD` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `MAJOR_TYPE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SALARY_STANDARD_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SALARY_STANDARD_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SALARY_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `DEMAND_SALARY_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `PAID_SALARY_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `MAJOR_CHANGE_AMOUNT` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `BONUS_AMOUNT` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `TRAINING_AMOUNT` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `HISTORY_RECORDS` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FAMILY_MEMBERSHIP` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REMARK` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PICTURE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ATTACHMENT_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `FILE_CHANGE_AMOUNT` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `REGISTER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHANGER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHANGER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHECK_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHANGE_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `LATELY_CHANGE_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `DELETE_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `RECOVERY_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `EXCEL_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '2',
  `CHANGE_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `MAJOR_CHANGE_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `TRAINING_CHECK_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `BONUS_CHECK_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `LICENSE_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PERSONAL_WORK_AMOUNT` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PERSONAL_ACHIEVEMENT_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `PAID_PERSONAL_ACHIEVEMENT_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `PERSONAL_EXPENSES_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `PAID_PERSONAL_EXPENSES_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `PERSONAL_WORK_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `GATHERED_PERSONAL_WORK_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `CREDIT_YES_OR_NOT_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `SALE_BONUS_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `SALE_BONUS_PAID_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `ORDER_DISCOUNT` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `RETAIL_DISCOUNT` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `CREDIT_DISCOUNT` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `draft_view`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `draft_view` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `MODULE_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reason` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PARENT_CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ACTIVE_STATUS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Y',
  `HREFLINK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_ID` varchar(255) DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_NAME` varchar(255) DEFAULT '',
  `DETAILS_TAG` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `HUMAN_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_PATH` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PICTURE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `WORKFLOW_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- 导出表中的数据 `draft_view`
--


-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `drag_img`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `drag_img` (
  `id` int(30) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `firstworkname` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `nickname` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `firstworkid` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `drag_img_top` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `drag_img_left` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `drag_img_name` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `drag_text` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `link` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `img_id` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `tree_view_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `category` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `human_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `name` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `change_char` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '变更',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=54 ;

--
-- 表的结构 `ecommerce_contact`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `ecommerce_contact` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `TEL` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `fax` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `ADDRESS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `POSTCODE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `EMAIL` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `QQ2` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `QQ4` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REMARK` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `ATTACHMENT1` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_CHANGE_AMOUNT` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `REGISTER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHANGER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHANGER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHECK_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHANGE_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `LATELY_CHANGE_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `DELETE_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `RECOVERY_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `EXCEL_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '2',
  `CHANGE_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `CONTACT_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHAIN_ID` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHAIN_NAME` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE1` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE2` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE3` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE4` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE5` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE6` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE7` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE8` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE9` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE10` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE11` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE12` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE13` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE14` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE15` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE16` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE17` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE18` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE19` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE20` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `GAR_TAG` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `EXCEL_BATCH_TAG` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',

  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `MODULE_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=100 ;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `ecommerce_view`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `ecommerce_view` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `MODULE_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reason` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PARENT_CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ACTIVE_STATUS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Y',
  `HREFLINK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_ID` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `FILE_NAME` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `DETAILS_TAG` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `HUMAN_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_PATH` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PICTURE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `WORKFLOW_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=83 ;

-- 导出表中的数据 `ecommerce_view`
--

--
-- 表的结构 `ecommerce_web_base`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `ecommerce_web_base` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `unit_id` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `name` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `title` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment1` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment2` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `advertisement1` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `advertisement2` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `content` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `copyright` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `webmaster_email` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `home_page` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `common_page` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE1` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE2` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `register_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `register` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `register_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=2 ;

--
-- 导出表中的数据 `ecommerce_web_base`
--

-- 表的结构 `ecommerce_web_template`

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `ecommerce_web_template` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `topic` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `filename` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment1` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE1` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE2` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `register_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `register` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `register_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `EXCEL_BATCH_TAG` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- 表的结构 `ecommerce_workflow`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `ecommerce_workflow` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `config_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `object_id` char(30) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `DESCRIBE2` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `checker_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `checker` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `check_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `TYPE_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=13 ;

--
-- 表的结构 `erpplatform_config_public_char`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `erpplatform_config_public_char` (
  `ID` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `KIND` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `TYPE_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE1` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `erpplatform_import`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `erpplatform_import` (
  `id` int(10) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `excel_batch_tag` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `col_name` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `col_nick` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `excel_tag` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `table_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `table_nick` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `no_submit_num` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `module_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `module_nick` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- 导出表中的数据 `erpplatform_import`
--


-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `erpplatform_moudle_design`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `erpplatform_moudle_design` (
  `id` int(3) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `VALUE` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `CATEGORY_ID` int(200) DEFAULT NULL,
  `PARENT_CATEGORY_ID` int(200) DEFAULT NULL,
  `ACTIVE_STATUS` varchar(255) DEFAULT 'Y',
  `HREFLINK` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `DETAILS_TAG` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `FILE_ID` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `FILE_NAME` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `MAIN_CODE` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reason` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `module_rank` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `picture` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `module_tablename` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- 导出表中的数据 `erpplatform_moudle_design`
--


-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `erpplatform_tree`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `erpplatform_tree` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `MODULE_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reason` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PARENT_CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ACTIVE_STATUS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Y',
  `HREFLINK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_ID` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `FILE_NAME` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `DETAILS_TAG` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `FILE_PATH` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHAIN_NAME` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PICTURE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `WORKFLOW_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=82 ;

  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,

  `reason` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PARENT_CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ACTIVE_STATUS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Y',
  `HREFLINK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_ID` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `FILE_NAME` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `DETAILS_TAG` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `HUMAN_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_PATH` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PICTURE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `WORKFLOW_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

  `CURRENCY_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `CURRENCY_MARK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CURRENCY_RATE` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `WAY_TAG` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CURRENCY_DECIMAL` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CURRENCY_TIME` date NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--

--
-- 表的结构 `finance_tree`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `finance_tree` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `MODULE_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reason` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PARENT_CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ACTIVE_STATUS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Y',
  `HREFLINK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_ID` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `FILE_NAME` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `DETAILS_TAG` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `FILE_PATH` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHAIN_NAME` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PICTURE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `WORKFLOW_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=80 ;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `finance_view`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `finance_view` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `MODULE_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reason` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PARENT_CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ACTIVE_STATUS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Y',
  `HREFLINK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_ID` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `FILE_NAME` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `DETAILS_TAG` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `HUMAN_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_PATH` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PICTURE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `WORKFLOW_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=443 ;

-- 导出表中的数据 `finance_view`
--

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `finance_voucher`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `finance_voucher` (
  `ID` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `VOUCHER_IN_MONTH_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHAIN_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHAIN_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `VOUCHER_TYPE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DEBIT_SUM` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `LOAN_SUM` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `ATTACHMENT_AMOUNT` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `SUMMARY` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `ATTACHMENT_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DEBIT_SUBTOTAL` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `LOAN_SUBTOTAL` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `DEBIT_OR_LOAN` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PRODUCT_AMOUNT` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `PRODUCT_PRICE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `NUMBER_IN_CASH_TABLE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REMARK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CURRENCY` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CURRENCY_RATE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DEPARTMENT` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PROJECT` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CUSTOMER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PRODUCT` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `ORDER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE1` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE2` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE3` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE4` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE5` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE6` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE7` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE8` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE9` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE10` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `ACCOUNTANT` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `ACCOUNTANT_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `ACCOUNTER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `ACCOUNTER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CASHIER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CASHIER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `CHANGE_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ACCOUNT_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `REGISTER_TIME` date NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01',
  `ACCOUNT_TIME` date NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01',
  `CHECK_TIME` date NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01',
  `DETAILS_NUMBER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHAIN_MATE_ID` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `TAX_RATE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `ACCOUNT_PERIOD` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PROFIT_OR_COST` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `COST_TAG` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PROFIT_TAG` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ITEMA_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `ITEMB_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `ITEMC_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `ITEMD_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SETTLE_WAY` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `ATTACHMENT_TIME` date NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01',
  `CHECKUP_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `DELETE_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `BANK_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `CASH_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `CORR_STOCK_TAG` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SETTLE_TIME` date NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01',
  `CASH_DIRECT` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `STOCK_DIRECT` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CASH_SUM` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DEBIT_SUBTOTAL_C` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `LOAN_SUBTOTAL_C` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `EXCEL_BATCH_TAG` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`ID`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- 导出表中的数据 `finance_voucher`
--


-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `fund_apply_pay`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `fund_apply_pay` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,

  `DEMAND_RETURN_TIME` date NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01',
  `ACCOMPLISH_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `REGISTER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `EXCEL_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PAY_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `RETURN_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `APPLY_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `CHAIN_ID` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHAIN_NAME` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FUND_CHAIN_ID` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FUND_CHAIN_NAME` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE1` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE2` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE3` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE4` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE5` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE6` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE7` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE8` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE9` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE10` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE11` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE12` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE13` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE14` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE15` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE16` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE17` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE18` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE19` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE20` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `GAR_TAG` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `EXCEL_BATCH_TAG` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `fund_tree` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `MODULE_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `FILE_NAME` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,

  `CHAIN_NAME` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `WORKFLOW_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=40 ;

--
-- 表的结构 `fund_view`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `fund_view` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `MODULE_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reason` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PARENT_CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ACTIVE_STATUS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Y',
  `HREFLINK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_ID` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `FILE_NAME` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `DETAILS_TAG` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `HUMAN_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_PATH` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PICTURE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `WORKFLOW_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=116 ;

--
-- 表的结构 `fund_workflow`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `fund_workflow` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `config_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `object_id` char(30) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE1` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE2` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `checker_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `checker` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `check_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PAY_TIME` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `GATHER_TIME` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

-- 导出表中的数据 `fund_workflow`
--

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `garbage_view`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `garbage_view` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `MODULE_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reason` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PARENT_CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ACTIVE_STATUS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Y',
  `HREFLINK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_ID` varchar(255) DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_NAME` varchar(255) DEFAULT '',
  `DETAILS_TAG` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `HUMAN_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_PATH` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PICTURE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `WORKFLOW_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- 导出表中的数据 `garbage_view`
--


-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `hr_bonus`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `hr_bonus` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `HUMAN_MAJOR_FIRST_KIND_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_MAJOR_FIRST_KIND_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_MAJOR_SECOND_KIND_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_MAJOR_SECOND_KIND_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `BONUS_ITEM` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `BONUS_WORTH` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `BONUS_DEGREE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REMARK` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `REGISTER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHECK_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `BONUS_TIME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE1` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE2` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE3` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE4` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE5` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE6` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE7` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE8` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE9` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE10` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE11` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE12` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE13` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE14` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE15` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE16` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE17` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE18` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE19` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE20` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `CHAIN_NAME` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `GAR_TAG` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `EXCEL_BATCH_TAG` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- 导出表中的数据 `hr_bonus`
--


-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `hr_config_file_kind`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `hr_config_file_kind` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `CATEGORY_ID` int(10) DEFAULT '0',
  `PARENT_CATEGORY_ID` int(10) DEFAULT '0',
  `CATEGORY_NAME` varchar(255) DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_ID` varchar(255) DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_NAME` varchar(255) DEFAULT '',
  `NICK_NAME` varchar(255) DEFAULT '',
  `REMARK` varchar(255) DEFAULT '',
  `DELETE_TAG` int(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `DETAILS_TAG` int(1) unsigned DEFAULT '0',
  `CHAIN_ID` varchar(255) DEFAULT '',
  `CHAIN_NAME` varchar(255) DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE2` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE1` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE3` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE4` mediumtext NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `COUNTER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=16 ;

--
-- 导出表中的数据 `hr_config_file_kind`
--

INSERT INTO `hr_config_file_kind` (`id`, `CATEGORY_ID`, `PARENT_CATEGORY_ID`, `CATEGORY_NAME`, `FILE_ID`, `FILE_NAME`, `NICK_NAME`, `REMARK`, `DELETE_TAG`, `DETAILS_TAG`, `CHAIN_ID`, `CHAIN_NAME`, `DESCRIBE2`, `DESCRIBE1`, `DESCRIBE3`, `DESCRIBE4`, `COUNTER`) VALUES
(1, 0, -1, 'all', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '');

--
-- 表的结构 `hr_file`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `hr_file` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `HUMAN_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_ADDRESS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_POSTCODE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_TITLE_CLASS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_MAJOR_FIRST_KIND_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_MAJOR_FIRST_KIND_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_MAJOR_SECOND_KIND_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_MAJOR_SECOND_KIND_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_BANK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_ACCOUNT` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_TEL` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_HOME_TEL` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_CELLPHONE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_EMAIL` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HOBBY` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SPECIALITY` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SEX` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `RELIGION` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PARTY` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `NATIONALITY` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `RACE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `BIRTHDAY` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01',
  `BIRTHPLACE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `AGE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `EDUCATED_DEGREE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `EDUCATED_YEARS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `EDUCATED_MAJOR` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SIN` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `IDCARD` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `MAJOR_TYPE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SALARY_STANDARD_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SALARY_STANDARD_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SALARY_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `DEMAND_SALARY_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `PAID_SALARY_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `MAJOR_CHANGE_AMOUNT` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `BONUS_AMOUNT` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `TRAINING_AMOUNT` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `HISTORY_RECORDS` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FAMILY_MEMBERSHIP` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REMARK` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PICTURE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ATTACHMENT_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `FILE_CHANGE_AMOUNT` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `REGISTER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHANGER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHANGER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHECK_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHANGE_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `LATELY_CHANGE_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `DELETE_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `RECOVERY_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `EXCEL_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '2',
  `CHANGE_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `MAJOR_CHANGE_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `TRAINING_CHECK_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `BONUS_CHECK_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `LICENSE_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PERSONAL_WORK_AMOUNT` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PERSONAL_ACHIEVEMENT_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `PAID_PERSONAL_ACHIEVEMENT_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `PERSONAL_EXPENSES_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `PAID_PERSONAL_EXPENSES_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `PERSONAL_WORK_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `GATHERED_PERSONAL_WORK_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `CREDIT_YES_OR_NOT_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `SALE_BONUS_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `SALE_BONUS_PAID_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `ORDER_DISCOUNT` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `RETAIL_DISCOUNT` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `CREDIT_DISCOUNT` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `CHAIN_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHAIN_NAME` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE1` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE2` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE3` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE4` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE5` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE6` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE7` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE8` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE9` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `C_DEFINE11` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE12` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE13` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE14` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE15` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE16` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE17` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE18` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE19` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE20` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `GAR_TAG` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `USED_TAG` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `EXCEL_BATCH_TAG` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `SALARY_TAG` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=13 ;

  `HUMAN_POSTCODE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `HUMAN_MAJOR_SECOND_KIND_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_MAJOR_SECOND_KIND_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

--
-- 表的结构 `hr_interview`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `hr_interview` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `DETAILS_NUMBER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `INTERVIEW_AMOUNT` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `HUMAN_MAJOR_FIRST_KIND_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_MAJOR_FIRST_KIND_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_MAJOR_SECOND_KIND_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_MAJOR_SECOND_KIND_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `IMAGE_DEGREE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `NATIVE_LANGUAGE_DEGREE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FOREIGN_LANGUAGE_DEGREE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `RESPONSE_SPEED_DEGREE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `EQ_DEGREE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `IQ_DEGREE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `MULTI_QUALITY_DEGREE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHECK_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `RESULT` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REMARK` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REMARK1` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `INTERVIEW_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `C_DEFINE1` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE2` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE3` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE4` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE5` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE6` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE7` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE8` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE9` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE10` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE11` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE12` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE13` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE14` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE15` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE16` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE17` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE18` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE19` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE20` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `EXCEL_BATCH_TAG` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- 表的结构 `hr_major_change`
--

  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `HUMAN_MAJOR_FIRST_KIND_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_MAJOR_FIRST_KIND_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_MAJOR_SECOND_KIND_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_MAJOR_SECOND_KIND_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `NEW_HUMAN_MAJOR_FIRST_KIND_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `NEW_HUMAN_MAJOR_SECOND_KIND_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `NEW_HUMAN_MAJOR_SECOND_KIND_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `SALARY_STANDARD_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SALARY_STANDARD_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SALARY_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `NEW_MAJOR_TYPE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `NEW_SALARY_STANDARD_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `NEW_SALARY_STANDARD_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `NEW_SALARY_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `REMARK1` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REMARK2` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `REGISTER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHECK_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `MAJOR_TIME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHAIN_ID` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHAIN_NAME` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `NEW_CHAIN_ID` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `NEW_CHAIN_NAME` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE1` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE2` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE3` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE4` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE5` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE6` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE7` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE8` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE9` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE10` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE11` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE12` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `HUMAN_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `IDCARD` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `TOTAL_POINTS` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `MAX_TOTAL_POINTS` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `TEST_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECK_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `EXCEL_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '2',
  `DESCRIBE1` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE2` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `EXAMTIME` time NOT NULL DEFAULT '00:00:00',
  `TEST_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `EXCEL_BATCH_TAG` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

  `CHAIN_NAME` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=91 ;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `hr_view`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `hr_view` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `MODULE_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reason` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PARENT_CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ACTIVE_STATUS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Y',
  `HREFLINK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_ID` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `FILE_NAME` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `DETAILS_TAG` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `HUMAN_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_PATH` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PICTURE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `WORKFLOW_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=623 ;

--
-- 表的结构 `intrmanufacture_view`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `intrmanufacture_view` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `MODULE_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reason` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PARENT_CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ACTIVE_STATUS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Y',
  `HREFLINK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_ID` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `FILE_NAME` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `DETAILS_TAG` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `HUMAN_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_PATH` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PICTURE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `WORKFLOW_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=437 ;

--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `intrmanufacture_workflow` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `config_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `object_id` char(30) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE1` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE2` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `checker_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `checker` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `check_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `INVOICE_TIME` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=2 ;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `logistics_view` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `MODULE_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reason` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PARENT_CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ACTIVE_STATUS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Y',
  `HREFLINK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_ID` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `FILE_NAME` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `DETAILS_TAG` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `HUMAN_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_PATH` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PICTURE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `WORKFLOW_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=270 ;

--
-- 表的结构 `logistics_workflow`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `logistics_workflow` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `config_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `object_id` char(30) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE1` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE2` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `checker_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `checker` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `check_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

-- 导出表中的数据 `logistics_workflow`

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `manufacture_module_balance` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `MANUFACTURE_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PRODUCT_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PRODUCT_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PROCEDURE_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PROCEDURE_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `MODULE_COST_PRICE_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `PROCEDURE_RESPONSIBLE_PERSON` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PROCEDURE_RESPONSIBLE_PERSON_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REASON` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHECKER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECK_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `REMARK` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
