-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `manufacture_workflow`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `manufacture_workflow` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `config_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `object_id` char(30) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE1` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE2` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `checker_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `checker` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `check_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `TYPE_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PROCEDURE_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `MODULE_TIME` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=12 ;

--
-- 导出表中的数据 `manufacture_workflow`
--

INSERT INTO `manufacture_workflow` (`id`, `config_id`, `object_id`, `DESCRIBE1`, `DESCRIBE2`, `checker_ID`, `checker`, `check_time`, `CHECK_TAG`, `TYPE_ID`, `PROCEDURE_ID`, `MODULE_TIME`) VALUES
(8, 68, '03020020080510100001', '09020001010100100000, ', 'admin, ', 'null', 'admin', '2008-05-10 18:23:37', 1, '02', '', 0),
(10, 62, '03040020080510100002', '09020001010100100000, ', 'admin, ', 'null', 'admin', '2008-05-10 18:46:46', 1, '03', '', 0),
(11, 63, '03050020080510100001', '09020001010100100000, ', 'admin, ', 'null', 'admin', '2008-05-10 19:44:07', 1, '04', '', 0);

--
-- 表的结构 `mold_assembly_installation`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `mold_assembly_installation` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `mold_id` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `assembly_item1` enum('OK','NG') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `assembly_item2` enum('OK','NG') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `assembly_item3` enum('OK','NG') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `assembly_item4` enum('OK','NG') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `assembly_item5` enum('OK','NG') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `assembly_item6` enum('OK','NG') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `assembly_item6_content` varchar(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `assembly_item7` enum('OK','NG') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `assembly_item8` enum('OK','NG') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `assembly_item9` enum('OK','NG') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `assembly_item10` enum('OK','NG') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `assembly_item11` enum('OK','NG') CHARACTER SET latin1 NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `assembly_item12` enum('OK','NG') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `assembly_item13` enum('OK','NG') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `assembly_item14` enum('OK','NG') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `assembly_item15` enum('OK','NG') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `installation_item1` enum('OK','NG') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `installation_item2` enum('OK','NG') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `installation_item3` enum('OK','NG') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `installation_item4` enum('OK','NG') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `installation_item5` enum('OK','NG') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `installation_item6` enum('OK','NG') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `installation_item7` enum('OK','NG') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `mold_ai_register` varchar(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `mold_ai_regist_time` varchar(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `mold_stock_checker` varchar(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `mold_stock_check_time` varchar(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `mold_installation_register` varchar(20) DEFAULT '',
  `mold_installation_regist_time` varchar(255) DEFAULT '',
  `mold_installation_checker` varchar(20) DEFAULT '',
  `mold_installation_check_time` varchar(20) DEFAULT '',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=DYNAMIC AUTO_INCREMENT=1;

-- 导出表中的数据 `mold_assembly_installation`

--
-- 表的结构 `mold_destruction`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `mold_destruction` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `mold_id` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `destruction_item1` enum('OK','NG') CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `destruction_item1_content` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `destruction_item2` enum('OK','NG') CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `destruction_item2_content` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `destruction_item3` enum('OK','NG') CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `destruction_item4` enum('OK','NG') CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `destruction_item5` enum('OK','NG') CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `destruction_item6` enum('OK','NG') CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',
  `destruction_remark` varchar(2000) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `mold_destruction_register` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `mold_destruction_regist_time` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `mold_destruction_checker` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `mold_destruction_check_time` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `destruction_item3_content` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `destruction_item4_content` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `spool_num` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8 DEFAULT '',
  `mold_life_ul` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8 DEFAULT '',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM  DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

-- 导出表中的数据 `mold_destruction`
--

--
-- 表的结构 `mold_destruction_pic`
--

  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `mold_id` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `pic_path` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8 DEFAULT '',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM  DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- 表的结构 `mold_exception`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `mold_exception` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `mold_id` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `exception_content` varchar(2000) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `exception_register` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `exception_regist_time` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `exception_checker` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `exception_check_time` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `mold_status` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM  DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- 表的结构 `mold_info`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `mold_info` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `mold_spec_id` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `mold_spec` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `mold_code` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `mold_type` smallint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `purchase_time` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `mold_location` smallint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `mold_life` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `mold_life_status` varchar(1) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `mold_machine_number` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `mold_hole_count` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `stock_time` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `assembler` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `assembly_time` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `top_mold_code` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `bottom_mold_code` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `lock_code` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `installer` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `installation_time` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `destruction_man` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `destruction_time` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `destroy_time` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `purchase2_time` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `mold_purchase_id` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `mold_purchase_supplier_id` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `product_spec_id` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `product_spec` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `product_count` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM  DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1 AUTO_INCREMENT=57 ;

--
-- 导出表中的数据 `mold_info`
--


-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `mold_purchase_order`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `mold_purchase_order` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `purchase_code` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `purchase_operater` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `purchase_time` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `purchase_supplier_id` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `purchase_count` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `purchase_register` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `purchase_register_time` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `purchase_checker` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `purchase_check_time` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `purchase_check_type` smallint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `purchase_ex_content` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM  DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1 AUTO_INCREMENT=51 ;

  `bottom_item2` enum('OK','NG') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NG',

  `mold_stock_checker` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `mold_stock_check_time` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET utf8 NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',

  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=30 ;

  `FILE_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=3338 ;

--
-- 表的结构 `notice_setting`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `notice_setting` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `notice_content` varchar(2000) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `is_enabled` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `notice_register` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `notice_register_time` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=DYNAMIC AUTO_INCREMENT=11 ;

--
-- 导出表中的数据 `notice_setting`
--

--
-- 表的结构 `oa_check_table`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `oa_check_table` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `tablename` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `main_kind_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `main_kind_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `first_kind_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `first_kind_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `second_kind_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `second_kind_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `init_file` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- 表的结构 `oa_regulation`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `oa_regulation` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `CHAIN_ID` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHAIN_NAME` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `regulation_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `subject` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `type` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CONTENT` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment1` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment2` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `remark` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `register` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `register_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHANGER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHANGER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `register_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHECK_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHANGE_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `LATELY_CHANGE_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `change_amount` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `C_DEFINE1` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE2` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE3` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE4` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE5` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE6` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE7` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE8` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE9` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE10` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE11` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE12` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE13` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE14` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE15` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE16` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE17` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE18` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE19` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE20` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `GAR_TAG` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `EXCEL_BATCH_TAG` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- 导出表中的数据 `oa_regulation`

--
-- 表的结构 `oa_regulation_dig`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `oa_regulation_dig` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `CHAIN_ID` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHAIN_NAME` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `regulation_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `subject` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `type` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CONTENT` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment1` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attachment2` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `remark` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `register` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `register_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHANGER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHANGER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `register_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHECK_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHANGE_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `LATELY_CHANGE_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `change_amount` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `C_DEFINE1` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE2` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE3` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE4` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE5` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE6` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE7` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE8` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE9` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE10` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE11` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE12` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE13` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE14` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE15` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE16` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE17` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE18` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE19` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE20` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `GAR_TAG` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `EXCEL_BATCH_TAG` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

-- 导出表中的数据 `oa_regulation_dig`

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `oa_tree`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `oa_tree` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `MODULE_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reason` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PARENT_CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ACTIVE_STATUS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Y',
  `HREFLINK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_ID` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `FILE_NAME` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `DETAILS_TAG` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `FILE_PATH` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHAIN_NAME` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PICTURE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `WORKFLOW_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=76 ;

--
-- 表的结构 `oa_view`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `oa_view` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `MODULE_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reason` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PARENT_CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ACTIVE_STATUS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Y',
  `HREFLINK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_ID` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `FILE_NAME` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `DETAILS_TAG` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `HUMAN_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_PATH` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PICTURE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `WORKFLOW_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=234 ;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `oa_workflow`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `oa_workflow` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `config_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `object_id` char(30) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE1` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE2` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `checker_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `checker` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `check_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `TYPE_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- 导出表中的数据 `oa_workflow`
--


-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `option_no`
--

  `no_type` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `description` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `register_time` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `product_middle_thickness_away` decimal(5,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',

  `front_E_away` decimal(5,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `back_10P0_away` decimal(10,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `back_E_away` decimal(5,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `attr1` varchar(2000) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attr2` varchar(2000) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `attr3` varchar(2000) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `plan_register` varchar(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `plan_register_time` varchar(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=5 ;

-- 表的结构 `package_info`
--

  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `product_spec_id` int(11) DEFAULT '-1',
  `product_spec` varchar(255) DEFAULT '',
  `mold_spec_id` int(11) DEFAULT '-1',
  `mold_spec` varchar(255) DEFAULT '',
  `package_pallet` varchar(255) DEFAULT '',
  `package_pallet_char` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `package_pallet_num` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `package_factory_pallet` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `package_count` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `package_weight` double(15,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `package_stock` varchar(100) DEFAULT '',
  `package_custom_id` int(11) DEFAULT '-1',
  `package_out_apply_status` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `is_dissolve` smallint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `is_out_stock` smallint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `stock_id` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `stock_name` varchar(50) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `stock_in_time` varchar(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `stock_out_time` varchar(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `package_in_apply_status` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- 表的结构 `plan_4_detail`

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `purchase_file_dig` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `PROVIDER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PROVIDER_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PROVIDER_NICK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PROVIDER_ADDRESS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PROVIDER_CLASS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `type` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PROVIDER_BANK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PROVIDER_ACCOUNT` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PROVIDER_WEB` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PROVIDER_TEL1` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PROVIDER_TEL2` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PROVIDER_EMAIL` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PROVIDER_FAX` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PROVIDER_POSTCODE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CONTACT_PERSON1` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CONTACT_PERSON1_DEPARTMENT` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CONTACT_PERSON1_DUTY` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

--
-- 表的结构 `purchase_tree`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `purchase_tree` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `MODULE_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reason` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PARENT_CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ACTIVE_STATUS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Y',
  `HREFLINK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_ID` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `FILE_NAME` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `DETAILS_TAG` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `FILE_PATH` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHAIN_NAME` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `purchase_view`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `purchase_view` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `MODULE_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reason` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PARENT_CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ACTIVE_STATUS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Y',
  `HREFLINK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_ID` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `FILE_NAME` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `DETAILS_TAG` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `HUMAN_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_PATH` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PICTURE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `WORKFLOW_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=217 ;

--
-- 导出表中的数据 `purchase_view`
--

--
-- 表的结构 `purchase_workflow`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `purchase_workflow` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `config_id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `object_id` char(30) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE1` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE2` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `checker_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `checker` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `check_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `INVOICE_TIME` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=3 ;

--
-- 导出表中的数据 `purchase_workflow`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `qcs_tree` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `MODULE_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reason` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PARENT_CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ACTIVE_STATUS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Y',
  `HREFLINK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_ID` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `FILE_NAME` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `DETAILS_TAG` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `FILE_PATH` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHAIN_NAME` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PICTURE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `WORKFLOW_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=144 ;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `qcs_view`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `qcs_view` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `MODULE_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reason` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PARENT_CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ACTIVE_STATUS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Y',
  `HREFLINK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_ID` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `FILE_NAME` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `DETAILS_TAG` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `HUMAN_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_PATH` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PICTURE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `WORKFLOW_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=128 ;

--
-- 导出表中的数据 `qcs_view`
--

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `qcs_workflow`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `qcs_workflow` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `CONFIG_ID` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `OBJECT_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE1` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE2` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECK_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- 导出表中的数据 `qcs_workflow`
--


-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `security_alive_access`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `security_alive_access` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `CHAIN_ID` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHAIN_NAME` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `EDITOR` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `MODULEC` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `TIME1` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `TIME2` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `MODULEI` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=2 ;

-- 导出表中的数据 `security_alive_access`
--

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `security_file_length`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `security_file_length` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `file_length` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=2 ;

--
-- 导出表中的数据 `security_file_length`
--

INSERT INTO `security_file_length` (`id`, `file_length`) VALUES
(1, 5.00);

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `security_license`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `security_license` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `HUMAN_MAJOR_FIRST_KIND_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `HUMAN_MAJOR_FIRST_KIND_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_MAJOR_SECOND_KIND_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `HUMAN_MAJOR_SECOND_KIND_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `HUMAN_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `LICENSE_CODE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `EXPIRY_PERIOD` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ENROLLMENT_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ACTIVE_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `type` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `unit_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHAIN_ID` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHAIN_NAME` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=13 ;

-- 导出表中的数据 `security_license`

--
-- 表的结构 `security_publicconfig_key`
--

  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `TABLENAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `COLUMN_GROUP` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=94 ;

--
-- 表的结构 `security_workspace`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `security_workspace` (
  `id` int(30) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `module_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `link` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `view_tree_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CATEGORY` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `human_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `name` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=80 ;

--

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `stock_apply_gather`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `stock_apply_gather` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `GATHER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `GATHERER_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `GATHERER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REASON` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REASONEXACT` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DEMAND_AMOUNT` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `ACCOMPLISH_AMOUNT` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `COST_PRICE_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `REMARK` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECK_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `REGISTER_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `DEMAND_RETURN_TIME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `ACCOMPLISH_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `REGISTER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `EXCEL_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `GATHER_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `RETURN_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `APPLY_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `NOT_RETURN_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',

  `CHANGE_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',

  `CHANGE_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `EXCEL_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '2',
  `SERIAL_NUMBER_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `COST_CALCULATE_TYPE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '移动加权',
  `CHAIN_ID` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHAIN_NAME` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE1` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE2` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE3` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE4` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE5` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE6` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE7` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE8` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE9` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE10` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

--
-- 表的结构 `stock_gather`

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `stock_gather` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `GATHER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REASON` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REASONEXACT` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REASONEXACT_DETAILS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DEMAND_AMOUNT` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `GATHERED_AMOUNT` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `COST_PRICE` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `COST_PRICE_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `GATHERED_COST_PRICE_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `REMARK` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECK_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `REGISTER_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `ACCOMPLISH_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `FINISH_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `REGISTER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `EXCEL_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '2',
  `GATHER_PRE_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `GATHER_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `LIST_PRICE` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `LIST_PRICE_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `QCS_APPLY_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `QCS_DEALWITH_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `QUALIFIED_AMOUNT` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `GATHERING_TIME` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `C_DEFINE1` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE2` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE3` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE4` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE5` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE6` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE7` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE8` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE9` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE10` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE11` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE12` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE13` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE14` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE15` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `C_DEFINE16` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE17` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE18` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE19` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `C_DEFINE20` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `GAR_TAG` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',

) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `stock_gathering` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `GATHER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DETAILS_NUMBER` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PRODUCT_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PRODUCT_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PRODUCT_DESCRIBE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `COST_PRICE` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `MAX_CAPACITY_AMOUNT` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `DEMAND_AMOUNT` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `AMOUNT` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `GATHERED_AMOUNT` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `AMOUNT_UNIT` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `SUBTOTAL` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `GATHERED_SUBTOTAL` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `STOCK_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `STOCK_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `NICK_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHECK_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `REGISTER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REGISTER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECKER_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REMARK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `SERIAL_NUMBER` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `STOCK_GATHER_GROUP_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `LIST_PRICE` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `stock_pay` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `PAY_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REASON` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REASONEXACT` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `REASONEXACT_DETAILS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DEMAND_AMOUNT` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',

  `FINISH_TIME` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',

  `CHECK_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `EXCEL_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '2',
  `PAY_PRE_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PAY_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PURCHASE_APPLY_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `MANUFACTURE_APPLY_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `APPLY_MANUFACTURE_AMOUNT_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `APPLY_PURCHASE_AMOUNT_TAG` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `LIST_PRICE` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `LIST_PRICE_SUM` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `QCS_APPLY_TAG` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PAYING_TIME` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `C_DEFINE1` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `C_DEFINE2` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `C_DEFINE5` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

--
-- 表的结构 `stock_paying`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `stock_paying` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `PAY_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DETAILS_NUMBER` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PRODUCT_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PRODUCT_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PRODUCT_DESCRIBE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `COST_PRICE` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `MAX_CAPACITY_AMOUNT` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `DEMAND_AMOUNT` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `AMOUNT` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `PAID_AMOUNT` double(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `AMOUNT_UNIT` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',

  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `MODULE_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reason` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PARENT_CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ACTIVE_STATUS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Y',
  `HREFLINK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_ID` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `FILE_NAME` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `DETAILS_TAG` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `FILE_PATH` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CHAIN_NAME` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PICTURE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `WORKFLOW_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=53 ;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `stock_view`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `stock_view` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `MODULE_NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `reason` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PARENT_CATEGORY_ID` int(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ACTIVE_STATUS` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Y',
  `HREFLINK` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_ID` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `FILE_NAME` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `DETAILS_TAG` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `HUMAN_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `NAME` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `FILE_PATH` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `PICTURE` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `WORKFLOW_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=670 ;

-- 导出表中的数据 `stock_view`
--

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `stock_workflow`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `stock_workflow` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `config_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `object_id` char(30) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE1` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `DESCRIBE2` text NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `checker_ID` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `checker` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `check_time` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '1800-01-01 00:00:00',
  `CHECK_TAG` int(1) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `GATHERING_TIME` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `PAYING_TIME` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 AUTO_INCREMENT=5 ;

-- 导出表中的数据 `stock_workflow`
--

(3, 0, '1', 'text', 'text', 'text', 'text', '1800-01-01 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0),
